# Developer Profile

> Copy this file to `.cursor/rules/local/my-profile.mdc` and fill in your settings.
> This file is gitignored — your settings stay local to your machine.
> See `docs/developer-setup.md` for detailed instructions.

## Environment

- **OS**: [windows | macos | linux]
- **Shell**: [powershell | bash | zsh]

## Communication

- **Language**: [ru | en]
  - When set to `ru`: respond in Russian, use Russian in comments and commit messages
  - When set to `en`: respond in English

## Terminal Commands

- **Command style**: always use [PowerShell | bash] syntax when suggesting terminal commands
- Example (PowerShell): `$env:VAR = "value"` instead of `export VAR=value`
- Example (bash): `export VAR=value` instead of `$env:VAR = "value"`

## Agent Behavior

- **Confirmation**: [yes | no] — ask for confirmation before executing multi-step plans
- **Verbosity**: [concise | detailed] — level of explanation in responses
- **Show diffs**: [yes | no] — show file diffs before applying changes
